tionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ecj1665702643547.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ecj1665702643547.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ecj1665702643547.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ecj1665702643547\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Output Channel (\n                              MsgChannel)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property specifies one or more information streams to be directed to the output box. There is no default value.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__p_d105575e1_d105576e1_d105577e1\">MsgChannel<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>}\n            {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,2</code>} {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,3</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Representation</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Compiler</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Messages issued by the compiler when compiling a component or analyzing a model.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Putmess</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Messages issued by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">putmess</span> ProcScript statement.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Message</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Messages issued by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">message</span> ProcScript statement.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">(default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecj1665702643547__table_d12470e1_d12471e1_d12472e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use the channel specified for the widget in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__section_l5m_qmc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d419350e221\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__p_d105581e1_d105582e1_d105583e1\">In ProcScript it is possible to specify a\n            comma-delimited list of numbers so that Output Box widget can simultaneously subscribe\n            to multiple channels, and (if applicable) unsubscribe from channels to which it was\n            subscribed before. In the Properties Inspector, it is only possible to choose a single\n            value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__p_d105584e1_d105585e1_d105586e1\">Compiler messages and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">putmess</span>\n            text are always directed to the message frame, but you can use  MsgChannel to also direct them to the Output Box.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__section_of4_rmc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d419350e238\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__p_d105590e1_d105591e1_d105592e1\">This property is static and can only be set in\n            ProcScript before the form is displayed (for example, before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span>\n            command in the exec operation).</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__pre_cdb_tmc_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n $fieldproperties(FLD4) = \"msgchannel=2,3\"\n edit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ecj1665702643547__section_c4g_tmc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d419350e253\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddd1665702643397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddd1665702643397.html\" title=\"The uoutputbox widget displays streaming text data. The data may come from a specified Output Channel, or be explicitly added. By default, it does not listen to any channel. Uniface provides a logical widget called OutputBox, which is mapped to uoutputbox.\">uoutputbox (OutputBox)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Output Channel ( MsgChannel) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Output Channel ( MsgChannel) This property specifies one or more information streams to be directed to the output box. There is no default value. MsgChannel = \" { 1 } { ,2 } { ,3 } \" Value Representation Description 1 Compiler Messages issued by the compiler when compiling a component or analyzing a model. 2 Putmess Messages issued by the putmess ProcScript statement. 3 Message Messages issued by the message ProcScript statement. (default) Use the channel specified for the widget in the .ini file. Description In ProcScript it is possible to specify a comma-delimited list of numbers so that Output Box widget can simultaneously subscribe to multiple channels, and (if applicable) unsubscribe from channels to which it was subscribed before. In the Properties Inspector, it is only possible to choose a single value. Compiler messages and putmess text are always directed to the message frame, but you can use MsgChannel to also direct them to the Output Box. Example: Setting in ProcScript This property is static and can only be set in ProcScript before the form is displayed (for example, before the edit command in the exec operation). operation exec $fieldproperties(FLD4) = \"msgchannel=2,3\" edit end; exec Copy Applies To uoutputbox (OutputBox) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}